channel.description:
ok well i port forwarded to my ip and everything and downloaded the no-ip duc and it still doesnt let anyone on. i dont get it at all and im a noob with routers :(.

ok so i made the services RSPS starting port 43594 and ending 43594 heres a pic of what options i get when i click add custom service [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img167.imageshack.us/img167/5044/routbf2.png[/img][/URL]
co owner on my server if you can help me get it up.
also. i have a switch would that affect anything? i have 3 computers downstairs that are all hooked up to a switch then the network cable ran upstairs and my dads computer is hooked up to the router and the cable from out switch is also.
